One Big European League¶

Lets predict if the top 5 leagues in European soccer played in one league all together who would win using information from this season. Since all the top leagues of paused for the world cup, it seems interesting to see if there was a world cup style season but with clubs from the top european leagues.

curr_team_stats_df = pd.read_csv('2022-2023 Football Team Stats.csv', sep = ';', encoding = "ISO-8859-1")
curr_player_stats_df = pd.read_csv('2022-2023 Football Player Stats.csv', sep = ';', encoding = "ISO-8859-1")

curr_team_stats_df.drop(columns = ['Pts/MP','xG','xGA','xGD','xGD/90','Attendance','Top Team Scorer', 'Goalkeeper'], inplace = True)
curr_player_complete_stats_df = curr_player_stats_df [['Squad', 'Goals','Min', 'Shots', 'SoT','PasTotCmp','PasTotAtt','Assists','PasAss','SCA','GCA','DriSucc','DriAtt']] 

for i,d in curr_player_stats_df.iterrows():
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'Goals'] = round((d['Goals'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'Assists'] = round((d['Assists'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'Shots'] = round((d['Shots'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'PasTotCmp'] = round((d['PasTotCmp'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'PasTotAtt'] = round((d['PasTotAtt'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'SCA'] = round((d['SCA'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'GCA'] = round((d['GCA'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'DriSucc'] = round((d['DriSucc'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    curr_player_complete_stats_df.at[i,'DriAtt'] = round((d['DriAtt'] * d['Min']) / 90)
    
curr_player_complete_stats_df = curr_player_complete_stats_df.groupby('Squad',as_index=False).sum()

curr_teams_df = curr_team_stats_df.merge(curr_player_complete_stats_df, how ='left', on = 'Squad')

curr_teams_df = curr_teams_df.assign(PassPerc = curr_teams_df['PasTotCmp'] / curr_teams_df['PasTotAtt'])

curr_teams_df = curr_teams_df.assign(DriPerc = curr_teams_df['DriSucc'] / curr_teams_df['DriAtt'])

curr_teams_df = curr_teams_df.assign(GoalsPG = curr_teams_df['GF'] / curr_teams_df['MP'])

curr_teams_df = curr_teams_df.assign(AssistsPG = curr_teams_df['Assists'] / curr_teams_df['MP'])

curr_teams_df = curr_teams_df.assign(WinPerc = (curr_teams_df['W'] + curr_teams_df['D'] * 0.5) / curr_teams_df['MP'])

curr_teams_df.drop(columns = ['MP', 'W','D','L'], inplace = True)
